g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後搞到幾個管理員一齊入嚟唔比佢用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實我想問咁停車場D阿姐用咩水喉幫住客洗車呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac8e4888d991764c0e65910182d37c224f54222c","tid":716804,"uid":75694,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T02:25:06.000Z","msg":"原告被告都係癡撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91793a9cc6187ff5b22e6f1c49929556d0536065","tid":716804,"uid":20815,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T02:31:30.000Z","msg":"睇完被告解釋，就知原告係痴撚線既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a800f3e066a5d71613bb6ec20b0f0ba22c28f3b","tid":716804,"uid":81670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3e155d52ce63f88e4abb596c3f2f180bbfafeec4","tid":716804,"uid":619,"like":106,"dislike":1,"score":105,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T00:27:01.000Z","msg":"我樓下都試過因為我哋十一點沖涼有水聲所以報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T02:32:24.000Z","msg":"我都係, 條友都痴線！<br />\n<br />\n警犬上到黎吠兩句就走."},{"pid":"f757714cdd9ebd3a18bd0f2fb0cbb4de5e4bf9d4","tid":716804,"uid":2613,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T02:36:24.000Z","msg":"住乜樓都好<br />\n最怕係有痴線鄰居<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前住嗰度，隔離嗰個真係痴線到<br />\n以為全部人都係針對佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7731600b39ff4498e5605b8ac61e813f7c94832","tid":716804,"uid":45170,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T02:39:39.000Z","msg":"上兩層 成日凌晨3 4點敲木板聲<br />\n一係就朝早 7 8點<br />\n有次上一層好似頂唔順 同